{"title":"九二重机枪（快板）","authors":["谢忠谋"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"九二重机枪（快板）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特务团二营机枪连  谢忠谋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呱打板一响开了腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表一表九二重机枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这枪本是日本造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂名字叫大仓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年抗战打日本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗缴获咱扛上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别的事情咱不表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱把那，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机件作用说端详；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一大部分尾筒底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若干小部配搭上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握把押铁传道板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有逆钩活笱簧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的作用管射击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拇指一压就开枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有闩子缓冲器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防止机关撞损伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一大部说完了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二大部紧接上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连发机管连发响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活塞上闩子和圆筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活塞杆内藏复坐簧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆筒内有撞针孔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有扒子钩和那压板簧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活塞捍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推动闩子圆筒前后闯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞针才能击发忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆筒作用更是大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞针按在正中央。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保管撞针不歪动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不歪不邪正当阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扒子钩压板簧用处不小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶着子弹送入弹膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拇指一压发了火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹壳蹦到平地上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大部分是尾筒部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小零件件件都说上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内有逆钩闩子室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标尺带座做的强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标尺升降螺杆高低分划"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转轮主板距离分划窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它前后来推动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标尺能升又能降。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上边有个眼镜座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装上镜子瞄准强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镜子座上带盖板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有螺丝管着逛档。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一件叫齿弧板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象锯条一般样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定高低来管上下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上下高低定的强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹴子体好象相公帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它管蹴出弹壳出枪膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第四大部是送弹机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碍子机，按配上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他管着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活塞杆后退停开关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送弹子座送弹子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪弹板拨到左边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送弹轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助枪弹板送子弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第五大部是油槽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油槽木是盛油的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上有毛刷油导子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给油板和诱导室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛刷油导把油抹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诱导室里有诱导子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油槽盖盖着油不漏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹴出口盖防尘土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第六大部是枪身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分成小部谈的真："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防热面来能放热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是其中一小部分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦斯漏孔作用大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦斯力量从此出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪筒内有来复线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弹旋转走的直。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第七大部有防热筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收容零件和放热的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上有机耳瓦斯筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防热面瓦斯规正器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"固定螺斗枪身紧定环，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧靠枪身固定的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦斯筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收容活塞杆前后动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推动连发起运动急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第八大部枪身孔架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳定枪身不能移。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞄准机件能高效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方向瞄准定位置。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第九大部升降轴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪身上下高或低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上有方向分划板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫射角度免差异。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第十大部脚头架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升降轴插在它腰里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升降转轮紧定杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前后三个脚柱子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一大部三只脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大腿插在脚头架内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架着枪身使用便利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各大部分对成块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能以打的敌人噢噢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的。同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我编这个快板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不为好听和好唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专为同志们好记的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大篇课文不好记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写成快板记容易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休把它当作寻常段，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是帮助军事学习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家今后多创作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟练掌握手中武器！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}